Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.08,0:01:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vegetables are not bad today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is an exciting time. In a moment,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hong Kong separated from its fatherland.\NA wanderer for half a century{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.61,0:02:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has finally gone back to her\Nmother to her love and embrace.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The whole world is watching this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone is anticipating\Nthe return of Hong Kong to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- the embrace of her motherland.\N- Mom, I'm back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiang Sheng, don't touch it. Put it back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I want to eat the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.29,0:02:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, let me have a small bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can't. This is for your father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad? Dad won't definitely\Nreturn for the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe he will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your father said that\Nhe will be home today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe that he will be back.\NYou are a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is a senior reporter. He's\Nbusy with the affairs of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have that much time\Nto keep us company. Eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiang Sheng! Jiang Sheng!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiang Sheng! Jiang Sheng!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, we already made an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up, Jiang Sheng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom, I'm going to play\Nwith Bei Xiao Wu first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it fun?\N- You are riding the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful. Dad is making a right turn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right turn.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Bei, can you be my horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No. My father is my horse.\NNo one else can ride on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's your horse? You ride on me every day.\NLet Jiang Sheng ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay, Dad.\N- Come, Jiang Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.46,0:04:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are riding the horse.\NWe are knocking into them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes.\N- It's fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, did you see my family?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you see my family?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, did you see my family?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor, did you see my family?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nurse! Nurse!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here, quick.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nurse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nurse, did you see someone\Nby the name of Jiang Liang?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there. Go over there and check now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you see someone by\Nthe name of Jiang Liang?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are busy. Check over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Look over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you see my family?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gave my family a big painful blow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect that my\Nchildhood would change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone said that my father and a female reporter from\Nthe provincial capital came her to conduct an interview.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At the same time, they had this kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's he? How is he related to my father?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mother didn't say anything.\NThey simply walked in silence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, one. One, two, one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiang Sheng, call him Older\NBrother in the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Greet him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your biological older brother in the\Nfuture. Address him as your Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Liang Sheng suddenly came into my world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Older Brother, what's in your bag?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't and also didn't know how to ask{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}why this boy, Liang Sheng,\Nsuddenly came to our home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:09:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could only determined\Nthat he's my older brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for me, I'm his younger sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, are you crying?\NAre you afraid of the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are afraid, I'm not.\NI will keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and eat. Sit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Liang Sheng, take your younger\Nsister into the house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Return my man to me. That's right.\NIt's your family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not leaving. I'm very sad. I want to\Nsettle score with his family. I want my man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will talk to them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Liang Sheng?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to get some water.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:14:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only interested in making quick bucks.\NThis is retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How it would be? Do we still\Nneed to talk about this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You will definitely be the\Nmanager in the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Uncle Bei.\NYou will be rich soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Liang Zi is really unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great. He's now crippled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Why did you step on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you. I heard\Nthat woman is his lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is the relationship\Nbetween that kid and Jiang Liang Zi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two. One, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, let's play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Older Brother, what are you doing?\NAre you going out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Older Brother, where are you going?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom said that this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.70,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, what's in your bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a music score.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.97,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a music score?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for playing piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.87,0:16:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A piano has lots of white
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and black keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They produces sound when you press on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, your shoes are really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sleeping together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- No need.\N- When I'm afraid of the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.51,0:17:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I would cover my head with the blanket\Nand I won't be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not afraid of the dark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were crying and you still said\Nthat you aren't afraid of the dark.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's crying?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weren't you crying just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eat now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:18:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, finish your food.\NI'm going to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the first time that I felt\Nthat my older brother was really nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at who this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, why is he sticking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my older brother. He's my\Nbiological older brother. Greet him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Biological older brother?\NWhere did he appear from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen that you have\Na biological older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom said that he could be your\Nfather's illegitimate child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bei Xiao Wu, you are talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I say the wrong thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't have the right to say this.\N- Why did you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bei Xiao Wu, bring it on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't. You won and Bei Xiao Wu lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could he do that? Let's\Nlook for his mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's your mother?\N- She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hit him? Did you hit him?\NGo and hit him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out here. The both of you, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.73,0:20:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong, Mother Bei?\N- Look at my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at my son. That wild kid hit him.\NWhat's going on? He hit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, did you hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He will hit others in the future and even kill\Nothers. He will also set fire. Isn't that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hit my son? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was beaten by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay at home and you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- You insisted on wandering out there.\N- What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want others to laugh at you?\NYou are really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you done yet? She's just a kid and\Nyou used the feather duster to hit her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying. Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going home or not? Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want everyone in the village\Nto notice you? Are you happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bei Xiao Wu scolded Older Brother.\NHe said that he's a wild kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We went to elementary school later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Liang Sheng! Jiang Sheng!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down. Let me take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.21,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you go to the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely wanted to cook a bowl\Nof noodles for Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.23,0:24:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so careless? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.45,0:24:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From that day on,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Actually, I knew that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.74,0:24:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't want me to cook.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.35,0:24:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You only knew how to cook noodles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.29,0:24:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thus, Liang Shen,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all those years, the noodles\Nthat you cooked for me,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.22,0:24:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it was your way of doting on me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.69,0:24:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.62,0:24:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:24:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.89,0:25:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open your eyes. You will know later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.58,0:25:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Older Brother, is this place pretty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.35,0:25:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.84,0:25:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have flower shops there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You still need to buy flowers? Look, there are so\Nmany flowers here and you still need to buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.79,0:25:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, do you know what I like most?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.34,0:25:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I grow up, I want to\Ngo to the flower shop too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.70,0:26:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, you have become much prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.00,0:26:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.36,0:26:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.48,0:26:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, these are for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.59,0:26:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.18,0:26:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.90,0:26:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng has grown up and matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.48,0:27:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.82,0:27:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.18,0:28:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.02,0:28:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The stars are falling from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.50,0:28:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These are not stars. They are fire flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.33,0:28:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are fire flies. I\Nread about them in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.79,0:28:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, why do\Nfire flies emit lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.38,0:28:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.45,0:28:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It's because its\Nmother is afraid that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.20,0:28:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it will lose his way. That's why, it\Nplaces a small light on its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.82,0:28:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.92,0:29:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.87,0:29:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We should release it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.10,0:29:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Can't it go home with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.07,0:29:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, its mother is looking for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.52,0:29:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire fly, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.31,0:30:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, I had a dream last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.63,0:30:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire fly found its mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.46,0:30:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.55,0:30:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.99,0:30:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiang Sheng, you are really foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.14,0:31:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.82,0:31:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you were born from your mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.58,0:31:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.99,0:31:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.26,0:31:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.59,0:32:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.57,0:32:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.22,0:32:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Where's your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.59,0:32:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.69,0:32:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.10,0:33:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think it is?\NYour family stole my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.86,0:33:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who stole this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me who stole this? Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.08,0:33:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Bei Xiao Wu gave this to me.\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.68,0:33:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You stole this and you\Nare still talking nonsense and lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.49,0:33:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you adults? He\Nstole my stuff and he still lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.52,0:33:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's wrong?\N- Manage your children.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.60,0:33:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He stole our stuff and he still lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.80,0:33:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you steal this? Tell your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.38,0:33:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bei Xiao Wu gave this to Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.90,0:33:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.83,0:33:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it be like this? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.82,0:33:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- It was a misunderstanding.\N- What do you mean? Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.86,0:33:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go home now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.73,0:34:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.39,0:34:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.50,0:34:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bei Xiao Wu gave this to Older Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.72,0:34:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Manage your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.40,0:37:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.90,0:38:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, do you want to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.82,0:38:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, do you want to eat?\NJust take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.00,0:38:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat it. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.78,0:38:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Really?\N- Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.97,0:39:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamed that I was playing\Nthe piano yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.77,0:39:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Older Brother, I want\Nto play the piano too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.73,0:39:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach you when you are older.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.99,0:39:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't separate them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.46,0:39:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Furthermore, if you separate them,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.56,0:39:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they will feel the pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.90,0:39:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.93,0:42:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not allowed to say\Nthat about my father.